            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card col-6">
            <div class="row p-5 pb-1">
                <div class="col-3">
                    <img src="/images/team/stan.png" class="w-100">
                </div>
                <div class="col-9">
                    <h2 class="text-uppercase">Stanislas Vandier</h2>
                    <p class="wb-text-secondary">{{ 'President of Wired Beauty'|trans }}</p>
                    <a href="#">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                        Linkedin
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <p class="p-5 team-desc">
                {{ '10 years at L’Oréal in marketing and general management positions in Europe.
